# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Fabric Visualizer — optional config
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# AI PARSE FEATURE
# Uncomment and set to enable AI-powered topology parsing from free text.
# Without this, the AI parse section is hidden and the form picker is the
# only input method (which is totally fine — the tool works great without it).
#
# Get a key: https://console.anthropic.com/
#
# SECURITY: Setting an API key here exposes it in the client-side bundle.
# This is acceptable for internal team tools with a spending-capped key.
# For public deployments, proxy the request through a tiny backend instead
# (see README "Production API key handling" section).
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
